                "invention-title": [
                    "Carbon nitride heterojunction and preparation method and application thereof",
                    "一种氮化碳异质结及其制备方法与应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a carbon nitride heterojunction and a preparation method and application thereof. A carbon nitride precursor is subjected to an ionothermal polymerization reaction in the presence of eutectic salt to prepare the carbon nitride heterojunction, the carbon nitride heterojunction comprises polyheptazine imine and polytriazine imine, and a heterojunction is formed between the polyheptazine imine and the polytriazine imine. The invention solves the problems of low interface matching degree and poor crystallinity of the carbon nitride heterojunction photocatalyst. The prepared high-crystalline atomic-level contact carbon nitride heterojunction has the advantages of being high in crystallinity, high in carrier transfer capacity and the like, the photocatalytic activity can be improved to the maximum extent, and the high-crystalline atomic-level contact carbon nitride heterojunction is expected to be applied to large-scale photocatalytic water decomposition hydrogen production, photocatalytic carbon dioxide reduction, photocatalytic nitrogen fixation, photocatalytic organic synthesis and other reactions."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种氮化碳异质结及其制备方法与应用。本发明将氮化碳前驱体在共晶盐存在的条件下进行离子热聚合反应，制得氮化碳异质结，该氮化碳异质结包括聚庚嗪亚胺和聚三嗪亚胺，所述聚庚嗪亚胺和聚三嗪亚胺之间构成异质结。本发明解决了氮化碳异质结光催化剂界面匹配度低和结晶性差的问题。本发明制备所得的高结晶原子级别接触的氮化碳异质结具有高结晶性和载流子转移能力强等优势，可最大限度地提升光催化活性，有望应用于大规模光催化分解水产氢、光催化二氧化碳还原、光催化氮气固定以及光催化有机合成等反应。"
                }
            ]
